to be a happy occasion.

30:13.930 --> 30:15.551
Yeah, for you and Angela.

30:15.651 --> 30:17.073
And you.

30:17.173 --> 30:19.155
We're all family, sweetheart.

30:19.255 --> 30:20.436
It doesn't matter.

30:20.536 --> 30:22.238
We don't even need
to talk about this now.

30:22.338 --> 30:23.479
You have other priorities.

30:23.579 --> 30:26.282
Lisa, you are my priority.

30:26.382 --> 30:29.285
Almost time to push.

30:29.385 --> 30:32.468
We'll finish this.
I promise.

30:42.879 --> 30:45.281
Hey.

30:46.602 --> 30:49.185
