a way out ♪</i>

31:00.696 --> 31:05.281
<i>♪ Stuck in the maze
that I call my head ♪</i>

31:05.381 --> 31:09.725
<i>♪ I'm going crazy over ♪</i>

31:09.825 --> 31:13.449
<i>♪ Things that I have
no control of ♪</i>

31:13.549 --> 31:15.331
<i>♪ Stuck in my mind ♪</i>

31:15.431 --> 31:17.533
<i>♪ A complex design ♪</i>

31:17.633 --> 31:19.535
<i>♪ On a merry-go-round ♪</i>

31:19.635 --> 31:22.098
<i>♪ I'm so done,
here we go again ♪</i>

31:22.198 --> 31:23.459
