31:29.245 --> 31:30.987
Look.

31:31.087 --> 31:32.148
Oh!

31:32.248 --> 31:34.390
Oh, my gosh!

31:34.490 --> 31:36.232
What am I seeing right now?

31:36.332 --> 31:37.914
Well, I don't know
about this Ivy chick,

31:38.014 --> 31:41.838
