to just be friends, but...

32:01.517 --> 32:05.341
as soon as I saw you, I--

32:05.441 --> 32:06.622
there was no question.

32:06.722 --> 32:08.144
I want you back.

32:08.244 --> 32:09.745
Like, I miss you.

32:09.845 --> 32:12.628
And I know you got a man,
so I don't mean any disrespect.

32:12.728 --> 32:16.873
But I hope he's coming correct.

32:16.973 --> 32:22.158
Because I know I am
for as long as it takes.

32:24.340 --> 32:27.443
I'm not losing you again.

32:29.305 --> 32:32.608
I think you just left me
speechless twice in one day.

32:32.708 --> 32:34.850
Well, then I'm off
to a good start.

32:34.950 --> 32:37.573
Thank you.

32:37.673 --> 32:40.576
All right, let me take a
photo of you in front of you.

32:40.676 --> 32:43.779
OK.

32:43.879 --> 32:45.141
Let's go. Come on.

32:47.803 --> 32:51.267
Hey, sorry to break
the news, brother,

32:51.367 --> 32:53.269
but you're stuck with me.

32:53.369 --> 32:55.671
What does that mean?

32:55.771 --> 33:00.116
Well, today,
remembering our history,

33:00.216 --> 33:02.858
seeing what we built...

33:04.780 --> 33:08.724
I'm always going to do what's
best for our firm's future.

33:08.824 --> 33:11.487
I promise.

33:11.587 --> 33:14.830
So no more secret meetings
for either of us?

33:16.592 --> 33:21.497
From now on,
it's just you and me.

33:24.960 --> 33:27.143
We'll take a look at
the terms of this acquisition,

33:27.243 --> 33:31.467
and we'll work it out.

33:34.610 --> 33:37.954
No matter what,

33:38.054 --> 33:41.597
I'm on your side.

33:41.697 --> 33:44.240
We started this together.

33:48.384 --> 33:50.806
Let's finish it together.

33:50.906 --> 33:53.129
Yeah.

33:59.195 --> 34:03.299
All these years, our history,
why didn't you come to me?

34:03.399 --> 34:05.181
Well, we're not in the habit

34:05.281 --> 34:07.143
