before making an offer.

34:07.243 --> 34:09.625
Oh, cut the bullshit,
Erika, out of respect.

34:09.725 --> 34:13.069
It's not like you
don't have a pattern.

34:13.169 --> 34:14.870
That was a long time ago.

34:14.970 --> 34:17.633
Oh, so you're not
the same woman who slept

34:17.733 --> 34:20.997
with her best friend's
boyfriend?

34:21.097 --> 34:23.639
I know that narrative
makes good gossip.

34:23.739 --> 34:25.361
But we both know
you and Phil were on a break

34:25.461 --> 34:26.682
when he and I started dating.

34:26.782 --> 34:29.485
You were my line sister.
In what world is that OK?

34:29.585 --> 34:31.007
Phil didn't have
a problem with it.

34:31.107 --> 34:32.008
We worked through that.

34:32.108 --> 34:35.491
Exactly,
because it was college.

34:35.591 --> 34:37.693
Everyone was on-again,
off-again.

34:37.793 --> 34:41.857
