for the next two years.

34:41.957 --> 34:43.419
We were an important relationship

34:43.519 --> 34:45.141
for each other, yes.

34:45.241 --> 34:49.625
But ultimately, things didn't
work out, and you got the guy.

34:49.725 --> 34:51.827
You won.
- Oh, I know.

34:51.927 --> 34:53.669
I just need to make sure that
moving forward

34:53.769 --> 34:57.973
whatever Phil decides,
you don't have another agenda.

35:00.216 --> 35:05.601
My interest in Philip
is strictly professional.

35:05.701 --> 35:07.363
You have my word.

35:09.105 --> 35:13.009
You better hope
that means something this time.

35:13.109 --> 35:15.891
<i>♪ Trying to find
it on the right track ♪</i>

35:15.991 --> 35:18.294
<i>♪ Oh, wanna be
just where the free at ♪</i>

35:18.394 --> 35:21.016
<i>♪ Hm, talk to Him,
He don't speak back ♪</i>

35:21.116 --> 35:23.379
Ahh, fuck!

35:23.479 --> 35:25.701
- Whoo!
- Whoo!

35:25.801 --> 35:27.383
<i>♪ Do this to my loved ones ♪</i>

35:27.483 --> 35:31.747
<i>♪ I've got some nerve ♪</i>

35:31.847 --> 35:33.869
<i>♪ Don't think I'm not sorry ♪</i>

35:33.969 --> 35:36.712
<i>♪ Hm, hear me now, hey ♪</i>

35:36.812 --> 35:38.874
<i>♪ This time I'm ready for it ♪</i>

35:38.974 --> 35:41.397
