35:41.497 --> 35:44.560
<i>♪ Can't stop this war in me ♪</i>

35:44.660 --> 35:46.762
<i>♪ Hm, I been here before ♪</i>

35:46.862 --> 35:49.965
<i>♪ Hm, h, I been here before,
