What the fuck?

37:12.548 --> 37:14.550
What the fuck?

37:50.666 --> 37:52.528
What happened?

37:52.628 --> 37:54.290
Um...

37:54.390 --> 37:55.691
uh...

37:55.791 --> 37:58.334
uh...

37:58.434 --> 38:00.336
Connor and I
were hanging out after school.

38:00.436 --> 38:01.697
OK, and?

38:01.797 --> 38:04.400
And um...

38:06.802 --> 38:09.745
And...

38:09.845 --> 38:12.588
and he has a fake.

38:12.688 --> 38:14.670
And so we grabbed a few beers.

38:14.770 --> 38:16.552
Oh, my--drinking?

38:16.652 --> 38:17.833
Carlton, really.

38:17.933 --> 38:19.074
I only had like,
half a beer, Mom.

38:19.174 --> 38:21.757
I swear, I swear,
and I wasn't even buzzed.

38:21.857 --> 38:23.839
But I was driving home,

38:23.939 --> 38:26.802
and I started
feeling nauseous

38:26.902 --> 38:29.204
and disoriented.

38:29.304 --> 38:31.447
And so I pulled over
to the side of the road,

38:31.547 --> 38:35.010
and I--I started walking.

38:35.110 --> 38:36.492
Right, I was walking.

38:36.592 --> 38:40.376
And I just kept
walking and walking.

38:40.476 --> 38:45.261
And I looked up, and I didn't
even know where I was.

38:45.361 --> 38:49.004
I don't even remember
where I parked the car, Mom.

38:50.486 --> 38:52.268
I left my phone
and wallet in there.

38:52.368 --> 38:55.030
And look,
I've had drinks before.

38:55.130 --> 38:56.632
But this was different, Mom.

38:56.732 --> 38:58.854
I swear.
This was something else.

39:00.616 --> 39:02.858
What do you mean?

39:04.460 --> 39:06.462
It was the meds.

39:08.544 --> 39:10.946
It had to be the meds, Mom.
I know it.

39:17.272 --> 39:20.175
We're going
to figure this out.

39:20.275 --> 39:21.897
OK, baby?

39:40.816 --> 39:42.598
Thanks for staying.

39:42.698 --> 39:44.320
Well, of course.

39:44.420 --> 39:47.122
I actually wanted to,
because the hospital Jell-O

39:47.222 --> 39:49.445
is super fire,
if you didn't know.

39:54.109 --> 39:56.111
You're a good friend.

39:57.152 --> 39:58.934
- So we're friends again?
- I didn't say all that.

39:59.034 --> 40:01.116
You sure?

40:05.561 --> 40:10.826
You know, my whole life,
it was me and my mom.

40:10.926 --> 40:15.030
And then I come out here, and
it's auntie, uncle, cousins.

40:15.130 --> 40:16.211
You know, you're going
from a family of two

40:16.211 --> 40:18.654
to a family of six
just like that.

40:21.176 --> 40:25.040
But family's still family,
even if they don't look

40:25.140 --> 40:28.724
like the one you're used to.

40:28.824 --> 40:30.886
Thanks.

40:30.986 --> 40:33.068
Yeah.

40:34.389 --> 40:35.651
You know, it takes
a lot of energy

40:35.751 --> 40:38.734
to keep making
yourself the outsider.

40:38.834 --> 40:41.156
Trust me, I know.

