41:56.872 --> 41:58.173
<i>So he lost his car?</i>

41:58.273 --> 42:00.656
You really believe this?
None of this makes sense to me.

42:00.756 --> 42:03.459
I know.

42:03.559 --> 42:07.342
But at least he did
the right thing by calling me.

42:07.442 --> 42:10.025
That's exactly
what we asked him to do.

42:10.125 --> 42:12.227
And combining
his meds with alcohol?

42:12.327 --> 42:14.029
That's just reckless.
He knows better than that.

42:14.129 --> 42:16.031
Yes, and we need
to talk to him about it.

42:16.131 --> 42:18.674
<i>But he admitted to drinking
when he didn't have to.</i>

42:18.774 --> 42:21.356
If we attack him for it, he'll
never tell us the truth again.

42:21.456 --> 42:24.439
And Dr. Richardson confirmed
that tapering off his meds

42:24.539 --> 42:26.241
could lead to an episode
like he experienced?

42:26.341 --> 42:28.403
Yes, I called him
as soon as I got home.

42:28.503 --> 42:30.766
<i>Disorientation, nausea,
some of his patients</i>

42:30.866 --> 42:32.648
<i>even experience vertigo.</i>

42:32.748 --> 42:34.750
So you believe
his story holds up?

42:36.111 --> 42:37.893
<i>Right now I do.</i>

42:37.993 --> 42:41.216
Do you really want to go out
there and call him a liar?

42:51.046 --> 42:52.708
Oh.

42:52.808 --> 42:56.512
I'm calm. I'm calm.
No, no, no, no, it's fine.

42:56.612 --> 42:58.834
I know what I did was stupid.

42:58.934 --> 43:02.077
The drinking, trust me,
I've learned my lesson.

43:02.177 --> 43:03.198
I never want to do that again.

43:03.298 --> 43:04.720
Yeah, well, you're lucky
it wasn't worse.

43:04.820 --> 43:05.961
It's been a long night.

43:06.061 --> 43:07.202
Yeah, I just
want to lay down.

43:07.302 --> 43:08.363
Yes, I'm going
to go with him.

43:08.463 --> 43:09.685
Look, I'm fine, Mom.

43:09.785 --> 43:12.267
No, you're far
from fine, Carlton.

43:18.473 --> 43:20.215
We're gonna be keeping
a closer eye on you.

43:20.315 --> 43:22.317
We all will.

43:48.864 --> 43:52.287
Look, I know you've got
a lot on your mind right now,

43:52.387 --> 43:56.151
but I have a bit
of news about Doc.

44:11.246 --> 44:14.449
Hey, you seen Jackie?

44:15.250 --> 44:17.252
She went home.

44:27.703 --> 44:30.385
Ah, fuck.

44:35.590 --> 44:38.814
Yo, Brian, where the hell
have you been, man?

44:38.914 --> 44:41.336
Look, I'm just here
to get my shit.

44:41.436 --> 44:43.298
Get your shit?

44:43.398 --> 44:45.701
Hey, look, man,
what's going on?

44:45.801 --> 44:47.382
Look, you better
tell me something,

44:47.482 --> 44:49.344
because nobody else will.

44:54.409 --> 44:56.872
Look, Doc is not
who you think he is.

45:11.626 --> 45:14.449
- Geoffrey, what's up?
- I've got some good news.

45:14.549 --> 45:16.732
I found your vehicle,

45:16.832 --> 45:20.715
completely out of gas
and sand on the seats.

45:23.158 --> 45:26.301
Hmm, uh, wow.

45:26.401 --> 45:30.225
Hm, on the corner
of Reseda and Victory.

45:30.325 --> 45:34.029
Any of this sound familiar?

45:34.129 --> 45:39.314
Uh, like I said, I was lost.

45:39.414 --> 45:42.437
But thanks.

45:42.537 --> 45:45.580
You know what
I find interesting?

45:49.104 --> 45:51.086
What's that?

45:51.186 --> 45:54.249
It was about 10 miles
between where your mother

45:54.349 --> 45:56.091
picked you up
and where I found it.

45:56.191 --> 45:59.835
Quite a distance
for someone traveling on foot.

46:01.356 --> 46:05.140
Um...

46:05.240 --> 46:07.302
I don't know, Geoffrey.

46:07.402 --> 46:09.264
I...

46:09.364 --> 46:10.385
I already
told my parents

46:10.485 --> 46:13.588
that I don't recall most

46:13.688 --> 46:15.951
of what happened
yesterday, so...

46:16.051 --> 46:18.954
Yeah.

46:19.054 --> 46:21.456
I'm aware.

46:30.986 --> 46:34.449
Sooner or later,
your truth will have no choice

46:34.549 --> 46:36.972
but to reveal itself.

46:37.072 --> 46:40.015
You know that, don't you?

46:54.289 --> 46:56.832
Yeah?

46:56.932 --> 46:59.314
- Hey, Uncle Phil.
- Hey, nephew.

46:59.414 --> 47:04.819
Hey, do you have time
to talk about Zenith and Doc?

47:13.548 --> 47:17.492
Yeah, so apparently,

47:17.592 --> 47:19.935
Doc has been taking bribes

47:20.035 --> 47:23.959
to steer players
to colleges and agents.

47:25.600 --> 47:28.143
And now
someone is threatening

47:28.243 --> 47:31.947
to blow the whistle
on Doc and the entire team.

47:32.047 --> 47:34.049
Hmm?

47:36.171 --> 47:37.592
Yeah.

47:37.692 --> 47:39.694
Have a seat.
